Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朋友  戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:27.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}2顆悸動的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因為不想傷害你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:37.30,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於是就連陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:41.35,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也再也無法照進來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:44.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明明就是奇跡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}邂逅也是戀愛也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.94,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}種子也是花蕾也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:58.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就連仍然青澀的果實也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:06.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}橙色  讓我想起了那天的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:08.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}兩個人的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:13.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就好像牽著手一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:15.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}橙子  何時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:17.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}才能變得甘甜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:20.52,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}還是會枯萎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:23.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要知道我的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:26.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}才全部全部吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好酸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:38.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然喜歡你  卻會哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:46.35,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想要早些成為橙色的果實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:49.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沐浴著你的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:53.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理想和夢想不斷膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:56.43,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快察覺到吧  吶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:23:00.03,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今天也品嚐了橙子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:03.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}依然酸澀  不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:06.92,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不能讓它像我一樣被丟棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:12.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部吃完了  喜歡你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:16.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好酸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.26,0:23:22.82,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}要哭了哦  喜歡你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.14,0:23:24.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜歡你哦

